{"tid":1954032,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[理論]如何借藍絲五毛去擴大我哋嘅勢力","createTime":"2020-04-01T13:54:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-04T06:12:30.000Z","uid":307203,"like":75,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":51,"replies":[{"pid":"98c6aea5c7f756d26ed1eea091e5e4e26278feb8","tid":1954032,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T13:54:52.000Z","msg":"事緣係有一條香城教育電視嘅片被藍絲同五毛去瘋狂dislike<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Dgj0xdl9qNk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DDgj0xdl9qNk&d=qkncW4ahWQk%2FJA9l97O%2FUg%2BnBs0jvEEXkL0KxwFTSeM%3D&h=80c899b2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Dgj0xdl9qNk</a><br />\n<br />\n而又被藍絲KOL同群組呼籲去做嘢<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gVtXae7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgVtXae7.jpg&h=57290eb6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n詳情可以睇返呢度<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有條黃色YouTube影片比藍絲dislike，但得400幾個like<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1953128\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1953128</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n到最後甚至連港共都出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n教育局 : 「香城教育電視」內容散播仇恨 勿讓孩童受不良意識荼毒<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1953847\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1953847</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n但係只有呢一條畀人騷擾過嘅片有好高嘅view 數， 其他都係維持返平時嘅幾百至到幾千左右嘅view <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KAAq3Bt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKAAq3Bt.png&h=8969c388&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />所以其實被佢哋騷擾之後，可以提高自己人睇嘅次數，甚至係成功打出同溫層(可能有啲藍絲繼續睇)，點睇都係擴大咗文宣嘅影響力<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">咁如何利用返藍絲五毛？</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">1. 喺佢哋主場煽風點火</span></span><br />\n<br />\n如果想主動出擊嘅話，可以直接喺佢哋啲Facebook pages/ groups，留圖、link 或者片<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果係被動，就睇佢哋諗住批鬥邊個，去附和就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">2. 通風報信</span></span><br />\n<br />\n如果佢哋真係開始做嘢，咁就即刻同手足通風報信，叫大家即刻去幫手，費事佢哋得逞<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">3. 雙贏</span></span><br />\n<br />\n到最後佢哋一失敗，一嚟打擊佢哋士氣，二嚟提升我哋曝光率，咁對我哋嚟講係win win situation<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">但係我哋要點樣防止佢哋用相同嘅方法搞我哋？</span><br />\n<br />\n記住Gphone 呢篇文就得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>【唔好再去建制Page俾嬲嬲 thx】<br />\n<br />\n琴日獲得最高曝光率，接觸最多Facebook 用戶￼嘅財政預算案Post 竟然係來自 #民建聯！🧨<br />\n<br />\n點解？因為當大家去佢哋個Post 洩憤俾嬲嬲😡同Comment 時其實係無意間推高緊佢嘅觸及率⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n按照Facebook 演算法（Algorithm）俾嬲嬲同留言不但比like 有更高嘅「影響力」仲會直接增加Facebook 推送該Post 嘅次數！<br />\n<br />\n你可能覺得俾多啲嬲嬲就會令到更多人知道保皇黨有幾賣港，但其實佢出得Post 就係想更多人知～<br />\n<br />\n🖍下次如果大家想追擊建制派嘅文宣，不妨Cap圖+評論再係自己ac手動轉載！<br />\n<br />\n#不要推廣建制文宣 #舉報都OK<br />\n<br />\n￼資料來源：HKG報 （大家記得唔好再比嬲嬲，令建制媒體可以自爽啦，btw，周融x1，thanks。）</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">總結：</span><br />\n<br />\n用毛澤東兩句說話簡單總結就係<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1. 我認為，對我們來說，一個人，一個黨，一個軍隊，或者一個學校，如若不被敵人反對，那就不好了，那一定是同敵人同流合污了。如若被敵人反對，那就好了，那就證明我們同敵人劃清界線了。如若敵人起勁地反對我們，把我們說得一塌糊塗，一無是處，那就更好了，那就證明我們不但同敵人劃清了界線，而且證明我們的工作是很有成績的了。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">2.戰略上藐視敵人，戰術上重視敵人</span><br />\n<br />\n最後希望大家睇完之後，可以幫手推一推，P牌仔推唔喐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bbe6eb49f205e1c1439a76505e1c5ab029608f7","tid":1954032,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T13:55:37.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"40373a050f8aba72c774d6f5cee496fabaed165a","tid":1954032,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T13:55:47.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"b9fa2feef65923a8450fb48b351b92323732b3b7","tid":1954032,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T13:55:58.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"ef043933c6a7a3cfbf838929a51556de7ad97b1c","tid":1954032,"uid":196701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"98c6aea5c7f756d26ed1eea091e5e4e26278feb8","tid":1954032,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T13:54:52.000Z","msg":"事緣係有一條香城教育電視嘅片被藍絲同五毛去瘋狂dislike<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Dgj0xdl9qNk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DDgj0xdl9qNk&d=qkncW4ahWQk%2FJA9l97O%2FUg%2BnBs0jvEEXkL0KxwFTSeM%3D&h=80c899b2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Dgj0xdl9qNk</a><br />\n<br />\n而又被藍絲KOL同群組呼籲去做嘢<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gVtXae7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgVtXae7.jpg&h=57290eb6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n詳情可以睇返呢度<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有條黃色YouTube影片比藍絲dislike，但得400幾個like<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1953128\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1953128</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n到最後甚至連港共都出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n教育局 : 「香城教育電視」內容散播仇恨 勿讓孩童受不良意識荼毒<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1953847\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1953847</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n但係只有呢一條畀人騷擾過嘅片有好高嘅view 數， 其