rge;\">1. 我認為，對我們來說，一個人，一個黨，一個軍隊，或者一個學校，如若不被敵人反對，那就不好了，那一定是同敵人同流合污了。如若被敵人反對，那就好了，那就證明我們同敵人劃清界線了。如若敵人起勁地反對我們，把我們說得一塌糊塗，一無是處，那就更好了，那就證明我們不但同敵人劃清了界線，而且證明我們的工作是很有成績的了。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">2.戰略上藐視敵人，戰術上重視敵人</span><br />\n<br />\n最後希望大家睇完之後，可以幫手推一推，P牌仔推唔喐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T13:57:35.000Z","msg":"笑死我<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4f52d653d833974b361e3389519d55704a183e0","tid":1954032,"uid":166080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T14:07:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9f3c1798f9b58f8cf8721e731028525c31b267a4","tid":1954032,"uid":272569,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T14:22:12.000Z","msg":"求幫手推下<br />\n<br />\n[幫手比料]英國國會將會調查香港警察打壓港人人權嘅狀況<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1953986\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1953986</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n另外有用post:<br />\n【終極回帶】抗爭裝備大整合！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1953920\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1953920</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n[721見] 如何正確隱藏身份 (整合+進階篇)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1327279\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1327279</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ca852ba524ea3075b4db956aeab6cdb8c012f556","tid":1954032,"uid":103243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T14:31:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6a63d6f6ce3b97b8225df13da978ea5bc68a2759","tid":1954032,"uid":161